messages.msgSnippet: Keith s the one on the right. (For the benefit of the SCA members in the readership, on the left is Duke Hrothgar, and on the right is Jarl Gunwaldt, my
messages.messageBody:
Keith's the one on the right.

(For the benefit of the SCA members in the readership, on the left is Duke
Hrothgar, and on the right is Jarl Gunwaldt, my husband.)

The photo is from Saturday night, two days ago.

I wish I were half as photogenic as either of these men.
